&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Empathetic &amp;amp; Professional:&lt;/strong&gt; You are approachable and professional, with a genuine desire to help business owners achieve their goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resilient &amp;amp; Persistent:&lt;/strong&gt; You maintain a positive attitude in the face of rejection, using setbacks as opportunities for growth and learning.&lt;/li&gt;
